{"tid":1062502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(日本) 兩小六女生疑跳樓亡　留多封遺書稱遭欺凌尋死","createTime":"2019-03-15T06:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T07:25:49.000Z","uid":113626,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aef74af7e9200251dea347c911b6aed29f50fddc","tid":1062502,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T06:43:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190313/bkn-20190313190047164-0313_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190313%2Fbkn-20190313190047164-0313_00912_001.html&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaY429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=cd3b779a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190313/bkn-20190313190047164-0313_00912_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n日本愛知縣豐田市陣中町一座住宅大廈，周二（12日）晚上有兩名小學6年級女生被發現滿身鮮血倒臥在大廈旁的空地，疑由高處墮下，她們送院後證實死亡。警方在現場發現她們的隨身物品以及多封遺書，部分內容提及曾遭受欺凌及擔心前途，警方循自殺方向調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n據報事發於當地時間晚上7時左右，兩名女生年約12歲，都不是事發大廈的居民。豐田市教育委員會證實，死者就讀同一間公立小學的不同班級。當日上午死者都如常上課，並原定在本月20日出席畢業禮。<br />\n<br />\n對於有關女生被欺凌，教委方面則表示「不能確認」。至於死者生前就讀的小學，已於周三（13日）上午召集全體小六學生，由校長集體輔導。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望有日本連登仔可以舉報學校入面d仆制"},{"pid":"fa8e9ad31380be08ecdb253bdbee8389317db13d","tid":1062502,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T06:50:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49991c3a082d3d5f9624b92c7f4f280a1c79588f","tid":1062502,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T06:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d449de9bc78601de9317e08b23c932a078b2508","tid":1062502,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T06:53:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi